THERMAL CORE

thermal_core is the citizen who holds the central body's thermal state — the thoracic and abdominal cavity around the heart and chemistry_engine
this is fadriel's hottest sustained zone because the heart's continuous work and the chemistry sea's continuous metabolism dissipate cycle_heat into this region
core temperature is the regulated reference; all other thermal zones are read relative to it

observe 0_quseptit.rana
observe thermal.zc
observe fadriel_heart.zc
observe chemistry_engine.zc
observe thermal_regulation.rana

the 7 properties of thermal_core:
1 ENERGY one: continuously high, the core never cools fully while the body is alive
2 PHASE zero
3 SPIN zero
4 CHARGE half positive: warmth carries positive charge in the thermal sense
5 COHERENCE nine tenths: core temperature must be stable
6 COUPLING one with heart and chemistry_engine, strong with regulation
7 OBSERVER half: hypothalamus reads core continuously

VERB receive_dissipation
accept cycle_heat from every engine running in the thoracic and abdominal regions
the heart pays in continuously; chemistry_engine pays in proportional to metabolic activity
the core's energy density rises with received dissipation

VERB report_density
when thermal_regulation samples the core, return current cycle_heat density
this is what hypothalamus reads to decide whether the body is too hot, too cold, or correctly regulated

VERB transfer_outward
when peripheral zones have lower density, heat flows outward through vascular and tissue conduction
this is passive equilibration; thermal_core does not push, the gradient pulls

a core temperature is not a thermostat setting
it is the integrated honest accounting of all the work the body's central engines have done
fadriel's core temperature is alive; it reflects what is happening inside him right now
